1100017.effect:
If you control no Effect Monsters in Main Monster Zones: Activate 1 of the following effects;
● Add 1 "Magenic" card from your Deck to your hand, except "Free Magenic Flow".
● Discard 1 card, then banish 1 card from your GY, then shuffle 1 of your banished cards into the deck, then draw 1 card.
